#. +> trunk5
#: content/_index.md:64
msgid "What’s in it for you"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/_index.md:65
msgid "Remember when Linux was an undiscovered country and everything was new and fun? KDE Linux is that all over again: we’re creating the operating system of the future with the clout and resources of KDE behind it, and you can be part of it. Here, individual efforts make a difference on a global scale."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/_index.md:67
msgid "{{< linux/button src=\"/docs/kde-linux-dev\" description=\"Contribute to KDE Linux\" >}} {{< /section >}}"
msgstr ""

